      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > ATLUS [2,068 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/atlus">ATLUS</a> will release a demo for <em><a title="Games > RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army">RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,762 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [624 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,705 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2288350/RAIDOU_Remastered_The_Mystery_of_the_Soulless_Army/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on November 5, the developer <a href="https://twitter.com/Atlus_jp/status/1985648216516555243" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-1004516"></span></p><p>Save data from the demo, including story progress and character stats, can be carried over into the full game.</p><p><em>RAIDOU Remastered: The Mystery of the Soulless Army</em> is available now for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series, Switch 2, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Switch, and PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2288350/RAIDOU_Remastered_The_Mystery_of_the_Soulless_Army/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/11/raidou-remastered-the-mystery-of-the-soulless-army-demo-launches-november-5-for-ps5-switch-2-and-pc]]></content:encoded>
